snippet.title: Outriders - Official Mantras of Survival Trailer | Game Awards
snippet.description:
Outriders shares some tips about how to best create the most carnage in People Can Fly's upcoming gonzo shooter. The new Game Awards trailers shares helpful hints like, cover is for cowards, to give you a sense of what it's going to be like to jump into Outriders' brand of mayhem.

#IGN #Outriders
